ANDROMEDA 6 

Runtime is now divided into different jobs, jobs.c, that accomidate more user control.
A structure of launch parameters are enclosed in the launch.tar file.

export LAUNCH={LAUNCHPAD_DIR}
Modify $LAUNCH/csh/go.csh to interface with your version of andromeda

::Execute in lowest directory inside launch::
$LAUNCH/csh/boot.csh 
do{
	$LAUNCH/csh/addStage.csh *ATTACK* *bandStage* *basisStage* found one
	$LAUNCH/csh/ritz.csh found one goSet
	$LAUNCH/csh/decompose.csh one one goSet
	$LAUNCH/csh/krylov.csh one one goSet
	--repeat with replacing found -> one and one -> two--
}while(!done)
